msgid "(You left a flower.)"
msgstr "（你留下了一朵鲜花。）"

msgid "Some building blocks."
msgstr "一些积木块。"

msgid "A sand bucket."
msgstr "一个沙桶。"

msgid "A stack of playing cards. They look handmade."
msgstr "一叠扑克牌。看起来是手制的。"

msgid "A gravestone lies here. You can't make out the name on it."
msgstr "这里有一块墓碑。你看不清上面的名字。"

msgid "There's a neatly written note taped to the back of the gravestone."
msgstr "墓碑背面贴着一张写得工工整整的字条。"

msgid "Read it?"
msgstr "要阅读吗？"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "It's been 5 years since your passing."
msgstr "你过世已经有5年了。"

msgid "I often wonder if things would have been different, had I been with you."
msgstr "我常常在想，如果我和你在一起的话，事情是否会有所不同。"

msgid "Would I have been able to protect you?"
msgstr "我会有能力保护你吗？"

msgid "Would I have died in your place?"
msgstr "我会愿意替你去死吗？"

msgid "I would have gladly accepted that resolution."
msgstr "我想我会毫不犹豫地接受这个提议。"

msgid "I wish I was strong and brave enough to fight for you."
msgstr "我希望我当时足够坚强和勇敢，能为你而战。"

msgid "But vengeance won't bring you back."
msgstr "但复仇并不能使你复生。"

msgid "I can only continue to warn everyone, and hope the locked site doesn't take another victim."
msgstr "我只能继续警告大家，并希望封锁区不会再有受害者。"

msgid "It's been quiet in the forest for the past few years."
msgstr "过去的几年里，森林一直很安静。"

msgid "But I know you always hated quiet."
msgstr "但我知道你一向讨厌安静。"

msgid "Please rest well."
msgstr "请安息吧。"

msgid "I'll visit you again soon."
msgstr "我很快就会再来看你。"

msgid "- Marzie"
msgstr "- 马尔齐"

msgid "A vase with fresh cut flowers."
msgstr "插有鲜花的花瓶。"
